law.history: Repealed 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 12, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1996; amended 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 343, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1996. -- Amended 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 3, effective February 17, 1994. -- Created 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 476, Pt. II, sec. 45, effective July 13, 1990.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Principals Assessment Center -- Assessment of principals required.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/96). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 12 prevails over its amendment in 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 343.
